WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: hWhniJTQsb0

NOTE Language: en

00:00:02.349 --> 00:00:10.589
Abraham Lincoln: I still have a dream. It is
a dream deeply rooted in the American dream.

00:00:11.133 --> 00:00:22.182
I have a dream that one day, this nation
will rise up, live out the true meaning of

00:00:22.182 --> 00:00:31.092
it's creed.We hold these truths to be self
-evident that all men are created equal.

00:00:31.092 --> 00:00:39.786
[APPLAUSE]

00:00:39.786 --> 00:00:49.982
I have a dream that one day on the Red Hills
of Georgia, the sons of former slaves and the

00:00:49.982 --> 00:00:57.497
sons of former slave owners, will they be able
to sit down together at the table of brotherhood?

00:00:57.497 --> 00:01:05.087
I have a dream, so let freedom ring from
the prodigious hill-tops of New Hampshire,

00:01:05.166 --> 00:01:12.326
let freedom ring from the mighty mountains
of New York, let freedom ring from the

00:01:12.326 --> 00:01:19.359
heightening Alleghenies of Pennsylvania, let
freedom ring from the snow-capped
Rockies of Colorado

00:01:20.049 --> 00:01:26.379
let freedom ring from the curvaceous 
slopes of California but not only that,

00:01:26.819 --> 00:01:36.701
let freedom ring from Stone mountain of
Georgia, let freedom ring from Lookout
mountain of Tennessee,

00:01:36.895 --> 00:01:45.365
let freedom ring from every hill and mole-hill
of Mississippi, from every mountain side,

00:01:45.365 --> 00:01:55.457
let freedom ring and when this happens,
when we allow freedom ring, when we

00:01:55.457 --> 00:02:02.002
let it ring from every village and every 
hamlet, from every state and every city,

00:02:02.519 --> 00:02:09.739
we will be able to speed up that day when all
of God's children - black men and white men,

00:02:09.739 --> 00:02:17.535
Jews and Gentiles, Protestants and Catholics,
will be able to join hands and sing in the words

00:02:17.535 --> 00:02:26.328
of the old Negro Spiritual, "Free at last, free at last,
thank God Almighty, we are free at last."

