00:03:42.530 --> 00:03:47.287
Shri Mataji: We have to say that, America
is a great country in the universe. It has

00:03:47.287 --> 00:03:55.300
the place of the Vishuddhi chakra, which
is the center of responsibility and discretion

00:03:55.300 --> 00:04:01.817
and they have been so responsible, so far.
They have given such noble ideas of democracy

00:04:01.817 --> 00:04:09.879
and of freedom and all those things which
are really all belonging to God's ideas

00:04:09.879 --> 00:04:15.863
and when they talk of all these things, we
must know that there is something much more

00:04:15.863 --> 00:04:20.027
that they can give to the whole world. So
many saints are born in this country

00:04:20.027 --> 00:04:24.310
because they realize that this is the
country where they'll be able to prosper

00:04:24.310 --> 00:04:29.879
better into their spirituality, so it is a
very great responsibility of Americans

00:04:29.879 --> 00:04:34.903
to understand that we have had great
leaders, we have had great noble ideas, we

00:04:34.903 --> 00:04:40.082
have got great saints living here - so many
are anxious to come down here. Only thing

00:04:40.082 --> 00:04:45.539
what we have to do, is to establish within
ourselves our Spirit and to be ready and

00:04:45.539 --> 00:04:50.518
prepared for this great tremendous work
that is going to come now and this is what

00:04:50.518 --> 00:04:56.605
the world has to do. If emancipation of
the humanity has to take place, it has to

00:04:56.605 --> 00:05:01.828
take place only from inside out and not 
outside in. Another thing I would like to

00:05:01.828 --> 00:05:07.551
tell that the danger is not from the outside
for America, not from anywhere else, it is

00:05:07.551 --> 00:05:13.516
from within themselves, so be careful. We
have to be careful about ourselves the way

00:05:13.516 --> 00:05:18.899
we are destroying. When we say, "What's wrong?"
we go headlong into our destructions.

00:05:18.899 --> 00:05:24.636
Human beings should not take freedom
as abandonment but freedom to enjoy

00:05:24.959 --> 00:05:30.679
completely and fully; The freedom that
takes you to a destruction, is not freedom

00:05:30.679 --> 00:05:35.837
and the right idea of freedom must be taken
and people should know that freedom,

00:05:35.837 --> 00:05:43.620
ultimate freedom is, when you become your
own master, when there are no habits, when

00:05:43.620 --> 00:05:47.939
you cannot be dominated by anything - you
are above everything - that's the freedom

00:05:47.939 --> 00:05:52.173
you have to achieve and that is why people
talk, long time back in this country,

00:05:52.173 --> 00:05:56.957
about freedom, they help all the countries
to get their freedom and now it is their

00:05:56.957 --> 00:06:03.212
job to get them their own freedom within
themselves, so that others will also follow.

00:06:03.212 --> 00:06:05.462
May God bless you all!
